yuma.

00:16:43.630 --> 00:16:46.530
I can't believe...
you're back.

00:16:46.530 --> 00:16:50.260
I heard you were
calling for me, so I came.

00:16:50.260 --> 00:16:54.490
I'm glad... you're here.

00:16:54.490 --> 00:16:57.460
Not that... I need
your help or anything.

00:16:57.460 --> 00:17:00.230
Everything's gonna be
okay cause astral's back!

00:17:00.230 --> 00:17:02.290
Great.

00:17:08.430 --> 00:17:09.860
Forget me.

00:17:09.860 --> 00:17:12.730
Destroy atlandis
before it's too late!

00:17:13.830 --> 00:17:15.490
It is time for zexal!

00:17:15.490 --> 00:17:16.960
Right!

00:17:16.960 --> 00:17:19.160
So, let's do this!

00:17:19.160 --> 00:17:23.960
Now you and I will build
the overlay network!

00:17:23.960 --> 00:17:26.860
What're they doin'?

00:17:30.230 --> 00:17:32.660
When two distant
souls become one,

00:17:32.660 --> 00:17:35.830
the power of zexal is revealed!

00:17:36.990 --> 00:17:39.930
Go zexal morph!

00:17:43.360 --> 00:17:46.290
Yuma and astral
just merged together!

00:17:46.290 --> 00:17:48.990
Let's get this done.

