00:18:29.190 --> 00:18:31.360
Get ready, utopia ray!

00:18:31.360 --> 00:18:35.930
Attack Atlandis now!

00:18:36.590 --> 00:18:39.160
Phoenix finish!

00:18:57.060 --> 00:19:00.930
The bond between yuma and astral
is stronger than I realized!

