00:19:10.260 --> 00:19:13.290
What will happen to him now?

00:19:18.860 --> 00:19:21.490
Whoa...

00:19:22.630 --> 00:19:23.930
Hey, look!

00:19:23.930 --> 00:19:25.560
It's the real world!

00:19:25.560 --> 00:19:28.460
And there's no sign
of that freaky trap!

00:19:28.460 --> 00:19:29.830
Then it can't devour us!

00:19:29.830 --> 00:19:31.590
in the end, we're all ok!

00:19:31.590 --> 00:19:33.830
I won the duel?

00:19:33.830 --> 00:19:35.830
Yuma...

00:19:35.830 --> 00:19:37.960
we have saved your world.

00:19:37.960 --> 00:19:40.390
Yeah, that was great teamwork!

00:19:40.390 --> 00:19:41.730
But...

00:19:41.730 --> 00:19:45.090
what about Trey?

