I finally understand, yuma.

00:19:58.560 --> 00:20:00.890
You accept me as I really am.

00:20:00.890 --> 00:20:02.390
I can see clearly now that

00:20:02.390 --> 00:20:05.060
you're the only
True friend I have.

00:20:05.060 --> 00:20:06.860
Look Trey, I'm sorry if I...

00:20:06.860 --> 00:20:09.790
yuma, I have a favor to ask you.

00:20:09.790 --> 00:20:13.890
Will you do what you
can to help save my family?

00:20:13.890 --> 00:20:15.630
If you just keep
"feelin the flow",

00:20:15.630 --> 00:20:19.090
I'm sure you'll find a
way to make things right.

00:20:20.590 --> 00:20:23.560
Trey!

00:20:23.560 --> 00:20:27.460
Goodbye...

00:20:31.160 --> 00:20:33.990
yuma!

00:20:33.990 --> 00:20:36.790
Alright, you won your
last heart piece just in time!

00:20:36.790 --> 00:20:39.860
So you made it to the finals!

00:20:39.860 --> 00:20:41.430
Yuma?

00:20:41.430 --> 00:20:44.790
I promise I'm not going to
let my friend Trey down.

00:20:44.790 --> 00:20:47.460
I will find a way
to help his family.

00:20:47.460 --> 00:20:50.490
There's no stopping me now!

00:20:51.660 --> 00:20:53.490
I failed you, vetrix.

00:20:53.490 --> 00:20:55.030
Forgive me.

00:20:55.030 --> 00:20:56.430
Everything will
be alright, Trey.

00:20:56.430 --> 00:20:57.760
I promise you.

00:20:57.760 --> 00:20:59.230
Vetrix, will you...

00:20:59.230 --> 00:21:01.630
hold my hand?

00:21:01.630 --> 00:21:03.290
That's much better.

00:21:03.290 --> 00:21:05.730
I think I'll try
to get some sleep now.

00:21:05.730 --> 00:21:07.760
Don't let your mind be troubled.

00:21:07.760 --> 00:21:09.990
Rest Well, Trey.

